{"tid":318492,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲有種空氣鳳梨","createTime":"2017-07-12T06:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T06:01:28.000Z","uid":63651,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8a132bd008d07473c857470ea3190e028a7bd573","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:19:55.000Z","msg":"因為我好寵佢，得閒帶佢出街曬太陽，又幫佢沖涼所以開係寵物台，勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲唔知咩係空氣菠蘿，以下是維基百科的介紹：<br />\n空氣鳳梨根部稀疏，外露在空氣之中，僅能作固定植株之用。葉片上長有會吸水的細毛，葉面的鱗片狀組織能夠吸收雨水或吸收空氣中的濕氣，是真正吸收水和養分的器官。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2189/2425286994_f8f1db5f85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffarm3.static.flickr.com%2F2189%2F2425286994_f8f1db5f85.jpg&h=f37c987e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之就係唔洗用泥種既植物，定時噴水同浸下佢就得～種係室內都無所謂架，但要比足夠陽光佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 植物殺手都唔洗太擔心，因為好易種，不過唔好以為佢係懶人植物就唔洗照顧，要淋水，唔係會死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n種係房都唔驚有蟲蟲，因為佢地好少蟲害，同埋無泥好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我個幾棵全部種係自己房<br />\n<br />\n有五百幾個原生品種，有d開花仲好靚添<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/readystar168/1380035753-3014973314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Freadystar168%2F1380035753-3014973314.jpg&h=2548793d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/1066000515a02ab7f7f8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F1066000515a02ab7f7f8&h=722ba59b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://0.share.photo.xuite.net/emily642157/1052411/10629578/493288775_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F0.share.photo.xuite.net%2Femily642157%2F1052411%2F10629578%2F493288775_m.jpg&h=44e59638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實好中意松蘿，但無露台種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/ackdbmt/1429811405-193497056_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fackdbmt%2F1429811405-193497056_n.jpg&h=436d0824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/angelachis/1339052473-420407885_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fangelachis%2F1339052473-420407885_m.jpg&h=8029818b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片全部網上搵，有興趣既巴絲可以google下或者交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ceb4df5a015435de482369794438bd01f7b385","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0501d7a5246eae3ed0cdd50d1198bb5cd2b9b9","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"邊到買？"},{"pid":"167d96d464c2b52406f52b4ee7d9b53900986a68","tid":318492,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"種過，種死左<br />\n都唔知點解個個都話好易種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36207d099d54cc335812d160e287ac809b6f4c27","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到買？</blockquote><br />\n花墟有得賣呀，不過得幾間有，但都幾易搵，行下就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得確實係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講年宵都會有"},{"pid":"a9179b19db50c993b5355a1dabc03ce827fc6348","tid":318492,"uid":946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊到買？</blockquote><br />\n花墟有得賣呀，不過得幾間有，但都幾易搵，行下就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得確實係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講年宵都會有</blockquote><br />\n係咪冇虫出現過? 想種個放室內"},{"pid":"090096d16b5a7630f58b2d969632b1a8cb3ef902","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>種過，種死左<br />\n都唔知點解個個都話好易種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好易種喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 空氣流通，散光（唔可以直曬陽光），一至兩日噴一次水就生得好健康"},{"pid":"13b1a2eb26935ba07910f7bc6b4302803d0feb4a","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>邊到買？</blockquote><br />\n花墟有得賣呀，不過得幾間有，但都幾易搵，行下就搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔記得確實係邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講年宵都會有</blockquote><br />\n係咪冇虫出現過? 想種個放室內</blockquote><br />\n種左兩年左右都無蟲患，但開花可能會易惹蟲啲，但佢好日都唔會開一次花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n種室內要確保空氣流通，同埋有陽光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果係office環境就唔係咁好，除非24小時冷氣"},{"pid":"95c869f5d8d2107ce43ae1b03ce0eadd56d2acaf","tid":318492,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd1fa590cf3e733aaf5d655f4f173df850e6055","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:52:38.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661deba90aaca7767c5f307b9a17a0dfb38d2a53","tid":318492,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:54:45.000Z","msg":"養貓唔敢種野<br />\n<br />\n利申 仙人掌都種得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234da11b4d8855743daa6605e9ef095bb81ab558","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>養貓唔敢種野<br />\n<br />\n利申 仙人掌都種得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都種死左仙人掌，不過空氣菠蘿係我手上生得好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7b4686716e5f252b8d107381a1486d6c189961","tid":318492,"uid":31382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:47:54.000Z","msg":"大概咩時候開花？<br />\n可唔可以落d開花肥料？<br />\n有蟲點處理？<br />\n<br />\n植物新手好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b1154c41c57e4cd9daecd39f476a09053b3268","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大概咩時候開花？<br />\n可唔可以落d開花肥料？<br />\n有蟲點處理？<br />\n<br />\n植物新手好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇係話多數春秋季開花，我種得最耐個棵死野兩年都未花比我睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係年年開花，同埋可能要種好耐先會開花，但我覺得依樣最好，因為比左好多心機悉心呵護之後先開花既感覺特別好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢一開花母株就唔會再生長，佢會生一株子株出黎（無性生殖）<br />\n亦都可以授粉用種子種（無試過），不過上網睇人講由於空鳳生長速度比較慢，種成年都係得個一毫咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以落肥料，開水稀釋噴上去就得，不過我無試過，反正唔施肥都可以健健康康，唔求佢地快快長大。唔太清楚，依個blog幾好，比條link你：<a href=\"http://twflowerangel.pixnet.net/blog/post/225616898-空氣鳳梨--tillandsia---常見q%26a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwflowerangel.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F225616898-%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E9%B3%B3%E6%A2%A8--tillandsia---%E5%B8%B8%E8%A6%8Bq%2526a&d=824RU93fzWklzC%2BX%2F3vUCdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=db9fea6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://twflowerangel.pixnet.net/blog/post/225616898-空氣鳳梨--tillandsia---常見q%26a</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打都試下種啦，唔洗好貴又易種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34fea924194140db7f3a3da55107488fcd33971","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:34:00.000Z","msg":"好文"},{"pid":"af96b4d5519372d7736ae943a5ae2b7a1d94b71a","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好文</blockquote><br />\n巴打又見到你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa6c5748f1fe332b2f5691f70c9e61dce1386b5","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:03:56.000Z","msg":"幫推！"},{"pid":"9367601077c4f5caca4c7ec323ee8266c64472e2","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好文</blockquote><br />\n巴打又見到你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhello 就黎搬新屋 搬完買黎養完寫份包膠比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598b98efd47d7e348555104914e70c50af8396f6","tid":318492,"uid":71389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>養貓唔敢種野<br />\n<br />\n利申 仙人掌都種得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都種死左仙人掌，不過空氣菠蘿係我手上生得好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n送過仙人掌畀人種過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61041a69ac2344e87954f4d85eb1e69b7bb0de39","tid":318492,"uid":54377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T08:17:59.000Z","msg":"有種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇種到開花<br />\n我行花墟見到人地個d開緊花<br />\n我個棵完全冇跡象開"},{"pid":"959fdd4a820d37635769be0a8330361882adee83","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:23:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好文</blockquote><br />\n巴打又見到你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhello 就黎搬新屋 搬完買黎養完寫份包膠比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8aeb1a6f1b226b0f48679f2fd479792dcc12025","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養貓唔敢種野<br />\n<br />\n利申 仙人掌都種得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都種死左仙人掌，不過空氣菠蘿係我手上生得好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n送過仙人掌畀人種過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問題黎？"},{"pid":"a34e7b8429a0b115ebad1ede39e498ae50ebade2","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:26:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有冇種到開花<br />\n我行花墟見到人地個d開緊花<br />\n我個棵完全冇跡象開</blockquote><br />\n我棵空可樂有開過花，但種左兩年既棉花糖無開過花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最想佢開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢好靚<br />\n其他都係種左半年左右，買返黎個陣好瘦好細棵，應該有排先會開花"},{"pid":"4e0f6d956f7592e789e6edf98cb99d4d1cc7b828","tid":318492,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455413a70c4468ae07c4a3d9645ecd1fb9e68993","tid":318492,"uid":71389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>養貓唔敢種野<br />\n<br />\n利申 仙人掌都種得死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都種死左仙人掌，不過空氣菠蘿係我手上生得好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n送過仙人掌畀人種過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問題黎？</blockquote><br />\n即係有送過仙人掌畀FD種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6978a12948d8b112be5a85d6d498c10f25b939a","tid":318492,"uid":10094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T09:49:48.000Z","msg":"幾靚喎 想係露台種d野有無咩植物推介 大細無所謂易種為主"},{"pid":"71f2a99b3a0f800a81483ae9ac61c3b79489eb2b","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T17:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾靚喎 想係露台種d野有無咩植物推介 大細無所謂易種為主</blockquote><br />\n仙人掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f853559f5512f3d4dc7f965d359ddbf345ee44","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幾靚喎 想係露台種d野有無咩植物推介 大細無所謂易種為主</blockquote><br />\n仙人掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仙人掌係方便易種，最主要夠陽光。如果露台夠曬既話種多肉都幾好，多肉bb好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我之前成日過度呵護浸死左棵野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以種多肉你都係上網睇下資料，唔好信我<br />\n如果露台唔係直照到太陽就可以種空氣鳳梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 空氣夠流通，但驚空氣太流通，太細棵既空鳳會被吹走，有朋友試過唔見左棵野，唔知係比風吹走定比雀叼走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他植物都唔係好知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係植物達人"},{"pid":"8ea077076499419b760b3fb0f9d4ae9e1add425a","tid":318492,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>幾靚喎 想係露台種d野有無咩植物推介 大細無所謂易種為主</blockquote><br />\n仙人掌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仙人掌係方便易種，最主要夠陽光。如果露台夠曬既話種多肉都幾好，多肉bb好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過我之前成日過度呵護浸死左棵野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以種多肉你都係上網睇下資料，唔好信我<br />\n如果露台唔係直照到太陽就可以種空氣鳳梨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 空氣夠流通，但驚空氣太流通，太細棵既空鳳會被吹走，有朋友試過唔見左棵野，唔知係比風吹走定比雀叼走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他植物都唔係好知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係植物達人</blockquote><br />\n香港種多肉最緊要係配啱疏水泥同充足陽光(唔需要中午12點直射咁勁, 反而係日照時間要夠長, 10hr+)<br />\n<br />\n我都有種松蘿(種咗成年, 今日先知佢叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n除咗噴水間唔中仲會噴花寶肥(粉肥開2000倍水), 種種吓一抽變兩抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過好似淨係開過兩朵花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ace14c4c7b825414f69265d59b5c50cd0c72e8f","tid":318492,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"我老母見到上面啲好幼嘅毛毛以為發霉<br />\n<br />\n掉左"},{"pid":"55db09fdb9bde65b98de36a70dd48e7e1729253d","tid":318492,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:05:26.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"3b1ac66c3f2f9166dc6d2172635c11d749a79acf","tid":318492,"uid":59839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:37:22.000Z","msg":"空氣草<br />\n<br />\n我屋企冇陽光入屋種唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a43da3a81250c461545d7ff35b2fc135b97712","tid":318492,"uid":109263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:09:11.000Z","msg":"其實佢啲吸收養份？"},{"pid":"87407f81430f19364fba4ad7c18392a4f0d150c4","tid":318492,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T19:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78317dd84f245f7dfcbee3c6d931a0a26095b94d","tid":318492,"uid":65888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:57:28.000Z","msg":"我試緊種街市d菠蘿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526c3670a272b3fe4dc9c0d11ffa2f00b2157f3a","tid":318492,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ceb4df5a015435de482369794438bd01f7b385","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:36:16.000Z","msg":"樓主最近點<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536f011da468883b23f682fd832450951675dc11","tid":318492,"uid":212294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:59:37.000Z","msg":"最近我手痕買一一堆黎養<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3034b0da228dcd1a6dd9ba8a7447ab54782548b","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536f011da468883b23f682fd832450951675dc11","tid":318492,"uid":212294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:59:37.000Z","msg":"最近我手痕買一一堆黎養<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"我死左棵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢乾咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能成日換地方"},{"pid":"daba31495f66594fb5f1e433533db5c60296dcc0","tid":318492,"uid":212294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3034b0da228dcd1a6dd9ba8a7447ab54782548b","tid":318492,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536f011da468883b23f682fd832450951675dc11","tid":318492,"uid":212294,"like":0,"dislike":0,